This is how to monotonic of l:
   When l's length is at least 1, then:
      The answer is 1
   End when

   Remember that up is 1
   Remember that down is 1
   Remember that i is 1

   Do this (diff of l's length and 1) times:
      Remember that a is item (diff of i and 1) in l
      Remember that b is item i in l

      When b is less than a, then:
         Remember that up is 0
      End when
      When b is more than a, then:
         Remember that down is 0
      End when

      Increase i
   End do

   When up is 1, then:
      The answer is 1
   But, if not:
      When down is 1, then:
         The answer is 1
      But, if not:
         The answer is 0
      End when
   End when
